query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci n pi t mi) */ select n.name
from person_info AS pi
inner join name AS n
on pi.person_id = n.id AND pi.info ilike '%japan%'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.person_id = n.id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info ilike '%adult%'
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.id = 3
inner join info_type AS it2
on pi.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info ilike '%birth%' group by n.name order by count(*) desc;
